views.markdown: If you need help with "Lotus Dark Additional", you can contact Caleb Rose, the developer, via e-mail.
Unknown is the maintainer of the package "Lotus Dark Additional". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "BananaManCJ" repo, Caleb Rose.
